**LEADERSHIP THROUGH TRANSITION  ·  BOOK ENTRY**

**Ego Is the Enemy**

Ryan Holiday  ·  2016

*Drawing on Stoic philosophy and historical example, Holiday argues that ego — the self built on recognition, title, and the approval of others — is the specific internal obstacle that prevents most leaders from doing their best work and surviving their hardest seasons.*

